    <display_title>
        NNStreamer Object Detection
    </display_title>
    <overview>
        <![CDATA[Object Detection showcases the Machine Learning (ML) capabilities ofi.MX SoCs by using a Neural Processing Unit (NPU). Object detection is the ML task that detects instances of objects of a certain class within an image. A bounding box and a class label are found for each detected object.]]>
    </overview>
